Package grafioschtrader.priceupdate.historyquote

Class HistoryquoteThruGTNet<S extends Securitycurrency<S>>

java.lang.Object
grafioschtrader.priceupdate.historyquote.HistoryquoteThruGTNet<S>
Type Parameters:
S - Security or Currencypair
All Implemented Interfaces:
IHistoryquoteLoad<S>
public class HistoryquoteThruGTNet<S extends Securitycurrency<S>> extends Object implements IHistoryquoteLoad<S>
Decorator that integrates GTNet historical price exchange with connector-based loading. This class wraps a HistoryquoteThruConnector and intercepts calls to first query GTNet servers for historical data, then falls back to connectors for unfilled instruments, and finally pushes connector-fetched data back to interested GTNet suppliers. Flow:
  1. Query PUSH_OPEN GTNet servers (prioritized, randomized)
  2. Query OPEN GTNet servers for remaining unfilled instruments
  3. Connector fallback for remaining instruments
  4. Push connector-fetched data back to suppliers that expressed "want to receive"
